---
---
<section class="emotional">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quote-card">
      <p>Hay tradiciones que merecen ser compartidas.</p>
      <span>Conoce el verdadero sabor de nuestra tradición.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 92px 20px;
  }

  .emotional {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--warm-white);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 22% 20%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.22), transparent 24%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 66%, rgba(217, 123, 168, 0.25), transparent 30%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--berry-dark), #2A0A1D 72%, var(--chocolate));
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1120px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-card {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
    border-radius: 38px;
    padding: clamp(28px, 6vw, 64px);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.14), rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.05));
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-card p {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.6rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .quote-card span {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.88);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    section {
      padding: 68px 16px;
    }
    .quote-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 26px;
    }
  }
</style>
